{
 "pages": [
  {
   "name": "page1",
   "elements": [
    {
     "type": "html",
     "name": "question1",
     "html": "<h4 style=\"text-align:center\"><b>\nUniversity of California, San Diego</b></h4>\n\n<br /><h4 style=\"text-align:center\"><b>\nScreening Script with Consent</b></h4>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:center\"><b>\nThe HEALthy Brain and Child Development (HBCD) Study</b></h4>\n\n"
    },
    {
     "type": "text",
     "name": "firstName",
     "visible": false,
     "title": "Potential Participant First Name",
     "hideNumber": true,
     "isRequired": true,
     "readOnly": true,
     "surveyVariable": "ParticipantVariable:firstName"
    },
    {
     "type": "text",
     "name": "lastName",
     "visible": false,
     "startWithNewLine": false,
     "title": "Potential Participant Last Name",
     "hideNumber": true,
     "isRequired": true,
     "readOnly": true,
     "surveyVariable": "ParticipantVariable:lastName"
    },
    {
     "type": "text",
     "name": "PSCID",
     "title": "Potential Participant ID",
     "hideNumber": true,
     "readOnly": true,
     "surveyVariable": "StudyInfoVariable:customId"
    },
    {
     "type": "text",
     "name": "question2",
     "title": "Person Conducting Screening Interview",
     "hideNumber": true
    },
    {
     "type": "expression",
     "name": "Today's Date",
     "title": "Date",
     "hideNumber": true,
     "expression": "today()",
     "displayStyle": "date"
    },
    {
     "type": "html",
     "name": "question3",
     "html": "<p style=\"text-align:left;color:black;font-size:16px\">We are currently looking for volunteers for a research study to learn more about the development of children as they grow from before birth to about 10 years of age. This is a nationwide study that will be the first large effort to look at how a child’s brain grows and develops in the early years of life and how the child’s environment influences that development. The study plans to enroll about 7,500 pregnant persons and their infants/children; about 300 will be enrolled from the San Diego area. </p>"
    },
    {
     "type": "html",
     "name": "question4",
     "html": "<p style=\"text-align:left;color:black;font-size:16px\">Would you like to hear more about the study?</p>"
    },
    {
     "type": "radiogroup",
     "name": "hearAboutStudy",
     "startWithNewLine": false,
     "titleLocation": "hidden",
     "hideNumber": true,
     "choices": [
      {
       "value": "item1",
       "text": "Yes"
      },
      {
       "value": "item2",
       "text": "No"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "type": "html",
     "name": "question5",
     "visibleIf": "{hearAboutStudy} = 'item1'",
     "html": "<p style=\"text-align:left;color:black;font-size:16px\">If you are invited to participate in the study, we would ask you to take part in completing questionnaires about yourself and your child, provide some biological samples from yourself and your child, and to permit your child to participate in brain imaging and other measures of their development. This would start now (in pregnancy) and we would ask to follow you and your child for the next 10 years. You will be paid for your time completing study visits.</p>"
    },
    {
     "type": "html",
     "name": "question6",
     "visibleIf": "{hearAboutStudy} = 'item1'",
     "html": "<p style=\"text-align:left;color:black;font-size:16px\">Is this something you would be interested in?</p>"
    },
    {
     "type": "radiogroup",
     "name": "interestedParticipation",
     "visibleIf": "{hearAboutStudy} = 'item1'",
     "startWithNewLine": false,
     "titleLocation": "hidden",
     "hideNumber": true,
     "choices": [
      {
       "value": "item1",
       "text": "Yes"
      },
      {
       "value": "item2",
       "text": "No"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "type": "html",
     "name": "question7",
     "visibleIf": "{interestedParticipation} = 'item1'",
     "html": "<p style=\"text-align:left;color:black;font-size:16px\">To find out if you might be eligible for the study, we would like to ask you a few questions about you, your pregnancy and lifestyle factors. Answering these questions will take about 10 minutes of your time. Some questions are personal, and you may feel uncomfortable answering them. You can choose not to answer any question or stop the screening at any time.</p>\n\n<br /><p style=\"text-align:left;color:black;font-size:16px\">Your participation in the screening is voluntary, and you won’t be paid for completing the screening. If you agree to this screening, we will enter your responses into a secure database so that we can better understand the population of pregnant persons who might be eligible for this study. All of the information you provide will be kept confidential.</p>"
    },
    {
     "type": "html",
     "name": "question8",
     "visibleIf": "{interestedParticipation} = 'item1'",
     "html": "<p style=\"text-align:left;color:black;font-size:16px\">Do you agree to go ahead with the screening questions?</p>"
    },
    {
     "type": "radiogroup",
     "name": "agreeToScreening",
     "visibleIf": "{interestedParticipation} = 'item1'",
     "startWithNewLine": false,
     "titleLocation": "hidden",
     "hideNumber": true,
     "choices": [
      {
       "value": "item1",
       "text": "Yes"
      },
      {
       "value": "item2",
       "text": "No"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "type": "html",
     "name": "question9",
     "html": "<p style=\"text-align:left;color:black;font-size:16px\">If asked, provide contact information for PI and the HRPP at UC San Diego.</p>"
    },
    {
     "type": "radiogroup",
     "name": "Eligibility",
     "visible": false,
     "title": "Eligibility",
     "choices": [
      {
       "value": "LLHopKBeMTi3mqPLL",
       "text": "Prenatal Completed - Waiting on Delivery"
      },
      {
       "value": "WGSS6PYWKGW4f3tSM",
       "text": "Potential Participant - Need to Contact and Screen"
      },
      {
       "value": "RRWtotQ5KhoKnEAYd",
       "text": "Not Interested"
      },
      {
       "value": "rBpE3FcP4zuWgczd6",
       "text": "Ineligible"
      },
      {
       "value": "8xJgtts7GXDpMFyXP",
       "text": "Lost to Follow up (no response)"
      },
      {
       "value": "M5X4D8uhgBANSioZ7",
       "text": "Active"
      },
      {
       "value": "iKtPL687Dbgiz2str",
       "text": "Completed Study"
      },
      {
       "value": "P45zgS6CK9gzxLEmi",
       "text": "Withdrawn"
      },
      {
       "value": "y8w78C2HTKF48jKwC",
       "text": "Lost to follow-up"
      },
      {
       "value": "vLA3RqnfeScwPbg3j",
       "text": "RA Unavailable/Missed - Reapproach"
      },
      {
       "value": "us2yCPaB8paNJfMB3",
       "text": "Holding Bin"
      },
      {
       "value": "P5RXhhxz6vLm8RF44",
       "text": "Eligible - Need to Contact and Consent"
      },
      {
       "value": "jg7P4qcB99EPygYJa",
       "text": "No Show - Reapproach"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "type": "text",
     "name": "globalID",
     "visible": false,
     "title": "globalID",
     "surveyVariable": "ParticipantVariable:globalId"
    },
    {
     "type": "expression",
     "name": "sublink",
     "visible": false,
     "expression": "\"https://hbcd.ripplescience.com/survey/rw4B2mgjhtwugqnXY/wfGAb7yBei9ubvfPg/form?pscid=\" + {globalID} + \"&firstName=\" + {firstName} + \"&lastName=\" + {lastName}"
    }
   ]
  }
 ],
 "triggers": [
  {
   "type": "setvalue",
   "expression": "{agreeToScreening} = 'item2' or {hearAboutStudy} = 'item2' or {interestedParticipation} = 'item2'",
   "setToName": "Eligibility",
   "setValue": "RRWtotQ5KhoKnEAYd"
  }
 ],
 "navigateToUrlOnCondition": [
  {
   "expression": "{agreeToScreening} == 'item1'",
   "url": "{sublink}"
  }
 ],
 "clearInvisibleValues": "none"
}

